org.bluez
Interface Error

All Superinterfaces:
DBusInterface
public interface Error
extends DBusInterface

Errors thrown by hcid or any bluetooth service. Created base on D-Bus API description for BlueZ bluez-utils-3.36/hcid/dbus-api.txt and bluez-4.32/doc/*.txt
